PRIME MINISTER
TRANSCRIPT OF THE PRIME MINISTER, THE HON P J KEATING
DOORSTOP, MYUNA COMMUNITY FARM, DOVETON, VICTORIA,
29 JANUARY 1996
E& OE PROOF COPY
Well, there you are, Gareth is as at home at Myuna Farm as he is with the
Cambodian peace accords, or chemical weapons. And what Mr Howard
would do, of course, is say " no, no, Mr Downer is better at this than he is".
Yes, sure, sure, sure he is.
